title: New Music Festival set for Nov. 3-5 (University of Wisconsin - LaCrosse)
text: ( Source : University of Wisconsin - LaCrosse) The UWL Music Department will host the 2015 La Crosse New Music Festival Tuesday-Thursday, Nov. 3-5. Concerts will be Tuesday and Thursday evenings in Annett Recital Hall , Center for the Arts.
